Arsenal left back Nacho Monreal took to Twitter to reveal his admiration for American film The Notebook.

Monreal stated his love for the 2004 romantic drama film  on Wednesday night - when England were playing Norway and Germany were taking on Argentina in a repeat of the World Cup final earlier this summer. 

The 28-year-old defender, who was left out of Vicente del Bosque's recent Spain squad, called The Notebook 'a very good film'.

