Released in 2004, The Notebook is a romantic drama starring Ryan Gosling and Rachel McAdams. 

Monreal has been involved in all five of Arsenal's competitive games so far this season as first choice left back Kieran Gibbs has been out injured.

Gibbs lasted just 53 minutes of Arsenal's Premier League opener against Crystal Palace before being forced off with a hamstring injury.

Monreal will be hoping he can keep his place for Arsenal's upcoming Premier League match against Manchester City on September 13.

 

